🎉Happy New Year! 
Clarity recently smacked me upside the head to make me see that I've been running my business in "survival mode" for the past 2+ years. At the beginning, I took things one day at a time and felt like I was doing okay. Somewhere along the way, I lost momentum. I'm a planner by nature, but planning ahead triggered fear and anxiety. 
Taking action helps me move through anxiety, so I'm building some momentum by planning for 2023.
💜Here's what's in the works:
🧵Online Workshops
✂️New quilt kits
🪡New and updated patterns 
I love all of you tons!!
#purpledaisiesquilting #quiltkits #modernquilts #penandpaperpatterns #sparrowsquilt by @penandpaperpatterns #puresolidsfabric #artgalleryfabrics @artgalleryfabrics

This was not the plan. Binding was the plan. 
The feed dogs won't stay up😩 when I switch them from being down. I'm investigating for an obvious reason before spending 💰💰on repairs. Anyone else have this happen to their Juki TL-2010?
@sewingdocandi should I just suck it up and take it in for service?
#jukitl2010q #ilovemyjuki

Took the bed off my machine and discovered the problem - the feed dog bar and spring are jammed up 😞. 
🤔 but I'm not sure how to fix it myself...
Stay tuned...
#jukitl2010q

Sewing success!!
A little extra cleaning and some oil on that stuck rod helped a ton!! I don't think it's a permanent fix, but it'll keep me sewing for now.

Edit: using WD40 was an act of desperation and is NOT recommended. Thankfully I used just a couple of drops and didn't spray it on. 
#jukitl2010q

My fingers hurt 
My hands hurt
My wrists hurt
I can't cut and sew for more than an hour or two at a time and it's breaking my heart. I've been struggling with this pain for 4+ years and I finally saw an orthopedic doctor last week. 
Good news 👉🏽 it's not arthritis 
Bad news 👉🏽 I have carpal tunnel and cubital tunnel syndromes in both hands/wrists.
A nerve test next week will tell how bad it really it and whether or not I need surgery.
Have you had this pain before? I'd love to hear what has helped you.

Love you all! Happy quilting🧵😘

#carpaltunnelsucks #cubitaltunnelsucks #ijustwanttosew
